                           (at least 5 tools were used: <term key="doubleCircle" ana="#doubleCircle">double circle</term>, <term key="doubleStraightLine" ana="#doubleStraightLine">double line fillet</term>, <term key="crissCross" ana="#crissCross"> crisscross</term>,
